#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:393 bd5e45aa3ee9492bb5a8f32af69be621
msgid "Can I run applications, like games, which require hardware acceleration?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:396 e36dcf86737743eb999e7c2b9baa8c85
msgid ""
"Those won’t fly. We do not provide GPU virtualization for Qubes. This is "
"mostly a security decision, as implementing such a feature would most "
"likely introduce a great deal of complexity into the GUI virtualization "
"infrastructure. However, Qubes does allow for the use of accelerated "
"graphics (e.g. OpenGL) in dom0’s Window Manager, so all the fancy desktop"
" effects should still work. App qubes use a software-only (CPU-based) "
"implementation of OpenGL, which may be good enough for basic games and "
"applications."
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:398 ca2966337f69406eb694d581312b0d35
msgid ""
"For further discussion about the potential for GPU passthrough on "
"Xen/Qubes, please see the following threads:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:400 c536eec34c0a4c7d84eb49bca7a7085f
msgid ""
"`GPU passing to HVM <https://groups.google.com/group/qubes-"
"devel/browse_frm/thread/31f1f2da39978573?scoring=d&q=GPU&>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:402 a6693ec523884667bda48cb9b633a090
msgid ""
"`Clarifications on GPU security <https://groups.google.com/group/qubes-"
"devel/browse_frm/thread/31e2d8a47c8b4474?scoring=d&q=GPU&>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:407 9edfc6dd428044c4bdc81eb66d5cc4bf
msgid "Is Qubes a multi-user system?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:410 0cbe8b92b96e461696454c7271aa1a41
msgid ""
"No. Qubes does not pretend to be a multi-user system. Qubes assumes that "
"the user who controls Dom0 controls the whole system. It is very "
"difficult to **securely** implement multi-user support. See `here "
"<https://groups.google.com/group/qubes-devel/msg/899f6f3efc4d9a06>`__ for"
" details."
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:412 d77b779e996649af82abc8b015322671
msgid ""
"However, in Qubes 4.x we will be implementing management functionality. "
"See `Admin API <https://www.qubes-os.org/news/2017/06/27/qubes-admin-"
"api/>`__ and `Core Stack <https://www.qubes-"
"os.org/news/2017/10/03/core3/>`__ for more details."
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:415 7b14937c047641d2bde4f483c86eeffc
msgid "What are the system requirements for Qubes OS?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction/faq.rst:418 46cea3faa7ce4d91921b9dad61ca1934
